OL,5, A man with cerebral palsy who was told 
OL,6, not to "play the disability card" in   
OL,7, his job at Home Bargains has received  
OL,8, #25,000 after alleging discrimination. 
OL,10,FRyan Walker, who worked as a sales     
OL,11,Fassistant at its Armagh shop, took the 
OL,12,Fcase after his duties were changed.    
OL,14,FHe had informed the firm that he needed
OL,15,Fto be physically active to manage his  
OL,16,Fdisability but he was later moved from 
OL,17,Fstacking shelves to working on tills.  
OL,19,FHome Bargains settled the case without 
OL,20,Fadmitting liability.                   
